            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Well, it looks there there are even MORE funky variations (in addition to the four funky holidays and the neon eyes). My guess is that these will be a part of the next mail in offer. I don't have any "connections" telling me this, its just a gut feeling. I wonder what other folks think. Does anybody KNOW?<br>
