            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I thought that the holiday variations and psycho eyes were enough, i really did...Do you guys know how much it costs to make a pez dispenser? SJ and Steph are selling these babies for 25 bucks a hit. Loose, they're 20 bucks. If there are 3000 of these ones too, and SJ has them all, you can expect them to make at least $60,000 bucks off of these. these variations are pulling in more cash than vintage dispensers...So i bet we can expect more variations after this, too. However they're REALLY getting these made, the variations are proving to be a goldmine for the Glews.</font>
          </td>
