            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">[And I'm sure that the dealers realize this. Note that SJGlew's web page hasn't been offering the new set of color variations for very long, but they're already offering the selling them at a discount -- 2 for $30 as an alternative to $20 apiece.]</font>
            <p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Just felt like pointing out that this special was available as soon as they received the new variations and before they were placed on the webpage.</font></p>
          </td>
